            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社21日專訊》翰森製藥(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03692:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03692\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03692-HK</a>)公布,截至2024年12月31日止全年純利43.72億元(<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>.下同),按年升33.4%,每股基本盈利0.74元,派末期息13.53港仙。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　期內收入122.61億元,按年升21.3%。(kl)</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">*有關業績的詳情,請參閱該公司之正式通告</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
